    "pathFromNamingConvention": false,
    "isRestful": true,

Explanation:
- No explicit route path is defined in this file. The index method exists, but there is no literal path binding here to determine a concrete API path.
- The handler is the controller method App\Http\Controllers\Api\V1\UserPostController@index, which processes the request.
- The implementation is in the same source file, so inSameFile is true.
- There is no path prefix, and there is no literal path string to extract, so both pathIsPrefix and pathFromLiteral are false.
- There is no explicit path derived from naming conventions in this file, so pathFromNamingConvention is false.
- The endpoint appears to be RESTful (a method returning a ResourceCollection for a list of posts), so isRestful is true.
- This entry is not for testing purposes, so isTesting is false.
